PrecisOrder (a) setting apart some 379.587 hectares of land in Saskatchewan for the OCHAPOWACE INDIAN BAND as Ochapowace Indian Reserves Nos. 71-1, 71-2, 71-3 and 71-4, and (b) consenting to the exercise by the SASKATCHEWAN POWER CORPORATION of its powers to expropriate land on Ochapowace Reserve No. 71-3 for the purposes of an electrical power transmission line.
